{"tid":1570681,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"野雞博士又share流料","createTime":"2019-09-15T07:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T08:29:29.000Z","uid":51620,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc1343db46d99989756175ddff10bb4ae0ace167","tid":1570681,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:51:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.701245323285019/2377080439034824/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkauyim%2Fphotos%2Fa.701245323285019%2F2377080439034824%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=afc90e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.701245323285019/2377080439034824/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69994028_2377080442368157_5580323228120776704_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQkmlhQ97cpxrCnfCm6GFsgtWGtyZns0q1aaIXYcR0jd5nNrcBk9joIvefERu-PNbCA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=dfd5bccd90f297649dd1d3fba9c8b231&amp;oe=5DFF49EE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69994028_2377080442368157_5580323228120776704_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQkmlhQ97cpxrCnfCm6GFsgtWGtyZns0q1aaIXYcR0jd5nNrcBk9joIvefERu-PNbCA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Ddfd5bccd90f297649dd1d3fba9c8b231%26oe%3D5DFF49EE&h=26592c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葛博士分享的內容是否真實，本傳媒不知道，文中沒有任何「示意圖」、「故事純屬虛構」之類。但相關分享的老人家大頭相及背影相片，是外國攝影師的作品，偷相證據確鑿。至於故事內容，大家可以去問葛博士及故事的原出處。<br />\n<br />\n還是那一句，任何沒有出處的圖片，都要小心。誤傳過的，請向傳給您的朋友及自己問責。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：(葛博士）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/121783367955302/posts/1677997142333909?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F121783367955302%2Fposts%2F1677997142333909%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=edbdf56f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/121783367955302/posts/1677997142333909?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n原出處：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/716780884/posts/10156702184765885?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F716780884%2Fposts%2F10156702184765885%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=05cd5469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/716780884/posts/10156702184765885?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n原圖出處：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/jadis1958/4229368046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flickr.com%2Fphotos%2Fjadis1958%2F4229368046&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=6672e565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.flickr.com/photos/jadis1958/4229368046</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qandrew.github.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqandrew.github.io%2F&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=1721c03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qandrew.github.io/</a><br />\n<br />\n分享全文：<br />\n//今日，有一個 83歲老婆婆自己一個人拖住兩箱剛開從超市買來的 energy bar和一個果籃來到警署探望警察。<br />\n<br />\n她看到我們雙眼就不斷地流著眼哭，不斷地說「亞Sir你們辛苦了」不停地感謝警察的付出。告訴我她有三個兒仔（年紀四十至五十）。她哭著說一生從末試過這麼心痛，這段時間沒有一個晚上可以睡得著。三個兒子一直駡她支持警察，她沒有和他們爭拗誰對誰錯。她要「身敎」惟有和兒仔們割席（因為不同立場）。<br />\n<br />\n可笑的是兒仔們還要吃家的、住家的、在家的小店工作賺錢。他們還去駡83 歳老媽。老媽一句「是我的錯⋯⋯沒有敎好你們⋯⋯請你們還給我1000元作為租用我的肚皮懷胎10月每月$100的租金，我馬上撤回當天生你們的決定⋯⋯⋯ 你們可以立即離開這個家⋯⋯這個家容不下你們 ⋯⋯你們去革命吧！」<br />\n<br />\n三個兒子不發一言，立刻收聲！<br />\n<br />\n回到家𥚃老太婆打電話給我說:「HabaSir 我這段日子，今天終於可以親身來感謝你們就是最開心，多謝你們香港警察。」//"},{"pid":"e8d34dcbee774023c6d4ab4312a83ffc7f4d2758","tid":1570681,"uid":22362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"呢d垃圾都做到議員真係"},{"pid":"9c2ac02bb86b368f48a19f5e8d81be56db049370","tid":1570681,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},